{"tid":466733,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母依家啲中學生係咪痴撚線架","createTime":"2017-11-12T23:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T19:28:53.000Z","uid":92376,"like":22,"dislike":890,"uniUserReply":135,"replies":[{"pid":"91bd806970de0169ca21c6c553ce5b1efecada75","tid":466733,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T23:55:19.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩落街，咁一出門口行到lift口見到有個中學生一樣等緊喎<br />\n咁令人扯火既事就發生喇，當我係十五樓<br />\n本身我係不以為意，諗住條細路棟左喺度應該識路呀嘛，點知就喺最後一刻部lift喺十六樓果陣我先留意到。。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母陰我，lift都唔識撳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩可能係咁岩十六樓都有人入我先趕得切撳，我真係想屌佢，但諗諗下家陣啲中學生係唔撚鬧得，一鬧就跳樓，所以都係稍為放佢一馬，不過佢個樣都知自己柒左架啦，希望佢下次醒目啲唔好咁戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d160ee6314015a8f4a86515488fdba54c4635c","tid":466733,"uid":16061,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T23:56:22.000Z","msg":"你肯定見到嘅係人？"},{"pid":"01ea5b7d9256ac493db99c28639ac19765dce8f0","tid":466733,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T23:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你肯定見到嘅係人？</blockquote><br />\n七點點有咁多鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18782e438ae6aa45146321b30e9d5e3223f52b1f","tid":466733,"uid":54930,"like":396,"dislike":2,"score":394,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T23:58:21.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"1d014256ea721d8049c011d2fd076adca4993bd2","tid":466733,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":226,"score":-219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T23:59:07.000Z","msg":"負評係做乜，覺得個細路唔抵屌？<br />\n邊個黎先邊個撳lift係約定俗成架啦<br />\n我真係唔知佢企喺度咁耐做乜鳩"},{"pid":"5d6b6f137383bb8c1ec990ecc17956b17ef0aeba","tid":466733,"uid":3072,"like":758,"dislike":8,"score":750,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:00:03.000Z","msg":"係咪我問題<br />\n睇咗幾次都唔明你嗡乜"},{"pid":"b8879245b0fce17c42dd106808371b91cbd1206d","tid":466733,"uid":16039,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:00:07.000Z","msg":"你自己唔識撳？<img src=\"/ass