s/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來都唔會有expect依樣嘢，信陌生人死得啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲廢老廢中會㩒多次就係知會有依啲情況出現，樓主危機意識連廢老廢中都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e8837e31f753304fbebc3e5c437f6878d8b019","tid":466733,"uid":74295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"真心唔知你講乜柒<br />\n睇撚左4次 <br />\n屌你老母詞不達意<br />\n上文又唔撚係接下文<br />\n仲撚要串柒柒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be03a9246f170282293898f3b9c5c5ac25deb5c","tid":466733,"uid":6436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:39:15.000Z","msg":"有時一個人諗緊其他嘢，真係會唔知自己做緊咩，佢應該係一時唔記得㩒，而唔係唔識/唔想㩒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc48aa95fcc2456b3060504b9723e2712cd1949","tid":466733,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完樓主解釋，再望返上面先明佢講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsorry係我無針對你地能力用左啲唔夠顯淺既表達方法，唔好意思我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1279082f762d2587106086daaca4a069f3eae4af","tid":466733,"uid":42064,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說岩岩落街，咁一出門口行到lift口見到有個中學生一樣等緊喎<br />\n咁令人扯火既事就發生喇，當我係十五樓<br />\n本身我係不以為意，諗住條細路棟左喺度應該識路呀嘛，點知就喺最後一刻部lift喺十六樓果陣我先留意到。。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母陰我，lift都唔識撳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩可能係咁岩十六樓都有人入我先趕得切撳，我真係想屌佢，但諗諗下家陣啲中學生係唔撚鬧得，一鬧就跳樓，所以都係稍為放佢一馬，不過佢個樣都知自己柒左架啦，希望佢下次醒目啲唔好咁戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譯：<br />\n樓主想搭lift落街，見lift口有個中學生，應該等緊lift。<br />\n<br />\n佢on99咁唔知個中學生冇撳lift，部lift就嚟到嗰時先發現。<br />\n<br />\n咁樓主on99，以為個中學生老馮都要撳lift俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩上一層有人入lift，反應遲鈍嘅佢先撳得切。如果唔係佢咁心靈弱小，發現自己lift都搭唔到嗰時，又話跳樓又剩，到時伯母傷心就唔好啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過佢個樣都知自己柒左架啦，希望佢下次醒目啲唔好咁戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8563b08764a4dc5c045d8da051f460a0f51042de","tid":466733,"uid":96170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬係表達得差嘅，但表達得<span style=\"color: red;\">差</span>同想屌人嘅事件係兩回事嘅。樓豬都唔駛咁嬲，我地都諗到好多原因會唔記得掀lift,唔好一碌鳩打一船人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"974c78870090b8c8a7f15c73a229697a032a0241","tid":466733,"uid":67367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:49:06.000Z","msg":"小兒麻痺？"},{"pid":"9c932dba6e556e02243ad02b2f4b86be30906967","tid":466733,"uid":89145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea6e356ce0dac71b3c6e6f8d18e328bbc4cd9200","tid":466733,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:52:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5488d4ce429abb3835019bfd26b9b8098a09fec","tid":466733,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:53:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c212dbc5f9167450b26739ba373160791b07b6d","tid":466733,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚野叫等lift唔識路呀1999</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180977ad6cfd71bc951ce99327e58c88036010ef","tid":466733,"