02:02:49.000Z","msg":"真心問樓主現實多唔多朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解可以自我中心到咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385c4d120ddd0f6f22f532e4c9e04483fd15068d","tid":466733,"uid":7365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"1日都唔知發生過幾多次啦<br />\n唔記得撳lift咋嘛<br />\n我都試過啦 都見過唔同年齡層既人試過<br />\n我又洗唔洗開幾個post屌唔同年紀既人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0313fadd2e865d5ff1a3db0e7fbecd01cd4ae340","tid":466733,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心問樓主現實多唔多朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解可以自我中心到咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4563364a7478de74753918f896b09af92c36b5eb","tid":466733,"uid":74532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"乜柒都屌"},{"pid":"b1c5ad047de7cf4c234069199358cf29fb2f2f8b","tid":466733,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話說岩岩落街，咁一出門口行到lift口見到有個中學生一樣等緊喎<br />\n咁令人扯火既事就發生喇，當我係十五樓<br />\n本身我係不以為意，諗住條細路棟左喺度應該識路呀嘛，點知就喺最後一刻部lift喺十六樓果陣我先留意到。。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母陰我，lift都唔識撳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩可能係咁岩十六樓都有人入我先趕得切撳，我真係想屌佢，但諗諗下家陣啲中學生係唔撚鬧得，一鬧就跳樓，所以都係稍為放佢一馬，不過佢個樣都知自己柒左架啦，希望佢下次醒目啲唔好咁戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譯：<br />\n樓主想搭lift落街，見lift口有個中學生，應該等緊lift。<br />\n<br />\n佢on99咁唔知個中學生冇撳lift，部lift就嚟到嗰時先發現。<br />\n<br />\n咁樓主on99，以為個中學生老馮都要撳lift俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩上一層有人入lift，反應遲鈍嘅佢先撳得切。如果唔係佢咁心靈弱小，發現自己lift都搭唔到嗰時，又話跳樓又剩，到時伯母傷心就唔好啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過佢個樣都知自己柒左架啦，希望佢下次醒目啲唔好咁戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於明樓豬條on9 up乜9<br />\n咁小事洗唔洗咁撚嬲</blockquote><br />\n1999專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b6c85c3a1df49aa0a2dc2b0cb8546c4bf79fd0","tid":466733,"uid":96790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:07:17.000Z","msg":"可能一時唔記得㩒姐<br />\n我自己試過，人地都試過<br />\n駛唔駛為左個制又屌又開post <br />\n你先痴撚線"},{"pid":"03d32c56a6ecf5af28612dec7c184815ee1fc351","tid":466733,"uid":6436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇撳lift姐, 可能唔記得左, 又或者好似有巴打咁講等緊人老母出門之類, 為左咁既事開post屌屌貢, 仲要標籤乜鬼中學生, 後生仔, 普通一個人唔記得撳lift姐, 你估真係捕撚住你幾點出門, 特登唔撳等你撳咩, 屌你老母都多鳩餘</blockquote><br />\n所以我都覺得樓主個思維好奇撚怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcae33afff5198a809e937f52a15a89de81f07c8","tid":466733,"uid":65773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"重點係<br />\n企在𨋢口就一定係等緊𨋢？"},{"pid":"b751d9f4a12523d718752a9b22b6618fc254d8d0","tid":466733,"uid":8733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇撳lift姐, 可能唔記得左, 又或者好似有巴打咁講等緊人老母出門之類, 為左咁既事開post屌屌貢, 仲要標籤乜鬼中學生, 後生仔, 普通一個人唔記得撳lift姐, 你估真係捕撚住你幾點出門, 特登唔撳等你撳咩, 屌你老母都多鳩餘</blockquote><br />\n所以我都覺得樓主個思維好奇撚怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假膠姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8af948774d85b852c39c46a0c4559dde19a8ac","tid":466733,"uid":43190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"等緊人得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189cb2e570c0bf25f3